import '../css/Classroom.css' function MyclassroomItem(props) { const userInfo = props.userInfo === undefined? {} : props.userInfo const selfClassroomStatus = props. return (
name: {userInfo.nickname}
profession: {userInfo.profession === undefined? "loading..." : userInfo.profession[0]}
status: 上線中
description:
time: / points: start
) } export default MyclassroomItem
